        <!-- Calculator card -->
        <section class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md" aria-labelledby="calc-title">
          <h1 id="calc-title" class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-2 text-slate-800">Ratio Calculator</h1>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Simplify ratios, solve proportions (<span class="pill">a:b = c:d</span>), scale a ratio to a target value, or split a total by a ratio.
            Built for speed, precision, and accessibility.
          </p>

          <!-- Mode selector -->
          <div class="mb-5">
            <fieldset>
              <legend class="sr-only" id="mode-legend">Choose calculator mode</legend>
              <div class="segmented" aria-labelledby="mode-legend" role="radiogroup">
                <input type="radio" id="mode-simplify" name="mode" value="simplify" checked><label for="mode-simplify">Simplify</label>
                <input type="radio" id="mode-proportion" name="mode" value="proportion"><label for="mode-proportion">Proportion</label>
                <input type="radio" id="mode-scale" name="mode" value="scale"><label for="mode-scale">Scale</label>
                <input type="radio" id="mode-split" name="mode" value="split"><label for="mode-split">Split Total</label>
              </div>
            </fieldset>
          </div>

          <!-- Panels -->
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <!-- Simplify -->
            <section id="panel-simplify" role="region" aria-labelledby="panel-simplify-title">
              <h2 id="panel-simplify-title" class="font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Simplify a ratio</h2>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div>
                  <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" for="simp-a">First term (a) *</label>
                  <input id="simp-a" type="text" inputmode="decimal" class="w-full border rounded-md px-3 py-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" aria-describedby="simp-a-err" aria-required="true">
                  <p id="simp-a-err" class="text-red-600 text-sm min-h-[1rem]" aria-live="polite"></p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" for="simp-b">Second term (b) *</label>
                  <input id="simp-b" type="text" inputmode="decimal" class="w-full border rounded-md px-3 py-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" aria-describedby="simp-b-err" aria-required="true">
                  <p id="simp-b-err" class="text-red-600 text-sm min-h-[1rem]" aria-live="polite"></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-3 mt-2">
                <button id="btn-simplify" type="button" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-md bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500">Calculate</button>
                <button id="btn-simplify-reset" type="button" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-md border border-gray-300 text-gray-800 font-semibold hover:bg-gray-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500">Reset</button>
              </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Proportion -->
            <section id="panel-proportion" role="region" aria-labelledby="panel-proportion-title" hidden aria-hidden="true">
              <h2 id="panel-proportion-title" class="font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Solve a proportion a:b = c:d</h2>
              <fieldset class="mb-3">
                <legend class="sr-only">Select the unknown term</legend>
                <div class="segmented" role="radiogroup" aria-label="Unknown term">
                  <input type="radio" id="unknown-a" name="unknown" value="a" checked><label for="unknown-a">a is unknown</label>
                  <input type="radio" id="unknown-b" name="unknown" value="b"><label for="unknown-b">b is unknown</label>
                  <input type="radio" id="unknown-c" name="unknown" value="c"><label for="unknown-c">c is unknown</label>
                  <input type="radio" id="unknown-d" name="unknown" value="d"><label for="unknown-d">d is unknown</label>
                </div>
              </fieldset>

              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div><label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" for="p-a">a *</label><input id="p-a" type="text" inputmode="decimal" class="w-full border rounded-md px-3 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" aria-describedby="p-a-err" aria-required="true"><p id="p-a-err" class="text-red-600 text-sm min-h-[1rem]" aria-live="polite"></p></div>
                <div><label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" for="p-b">b *</label><input id="p-b" type="text" inputmode="decimal" class="w-full border rounded-md px-3 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" aria-describedby="p-b-err" aria-required="true"><p id="p-b-err" class="text-red-600 text-sm min-h-[1rem]" aria-live="polite"></p></div>
              </div>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-2">
                <div><label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" for="p-c">c *</label><input id="p-c" type="text" inputmode="decimal" class="w-full border rounded-md px-3 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" aria-describedby="p-c-err" aria-required="true"><p id="p-c-err" class="text-red-600 text-sm min-h-[1rem]" aria-live="polite"></p></div>
                <div><label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" for="p-d">d *</label><input id="p-d" type="text" inputmode="decimal" class="w-full border rounded-md px-3 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" aria-describedby="p-d-err" aria-required="true"><p id="p-d-err" class="text-red-600 text-sm min-h-[1rem]" aria-live="polite"></p></div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-3 mt-2">
                <button id="btn-proportion" type="button" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-md bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500">Calculate</button>
                <button id="btn-proportion-reset" type="button" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-md border border-gray-300 text-gray-800 font-semibold hover:bg-gray-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500">Reset</button>
              </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Scale -->
            <section id="panel-scale" role="region" aria-labelledby="panel-scale-title" hidden aria-hidden="true">
              <h2 id="panel-scale-title" class="font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Scale a ratio to match a target</h2>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div><label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" for="sc-a">First term (a) *</label><input id="sc-a" type="text" inputmode="decimal" class="w-full border rounded-md px-3 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" aria-describedby="sc-a-err" aria-required="true"><p id="sc-a-err" class="text-red-600 text-sm min-h-[1rem]" aria-live="polite"></p></div>
                <div><label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" for="sc-b">Second term (b) *</label><input id="sc-b" type="text" inputmode="decimal" class="w-full border rounded-md px-3 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" aria-describedby="sc-b-err" aria-required="true"><p id="sc-b-err" class="text-red-600 text-sm min-h-[1rem]" aria-live="polite"></p></div>
              </div>

              <fieldset class="mt-2">
                <legend class="sr-only">Which term to set</legend>
                <div class="segmented" role="radiogroup" aria-label="Term to set">
                  <input type="radio" id="sc-pin-a" name="sc-pin" value="a" checked><label for="sc-pin-a">Set a to</label>
                  <input type="radio" id="sc-pin-b" name="sc-pin" value="b"><label for="sc-pin-b">Set b to</label>
                </div>
              </fieldset>

              <div class="mt-2">
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" for="sc-target">Target value *</label>
                <input id="sc-target" type="text" inputmode="decimal" class="w-full border rounded-md px-3 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" aria-describedby="sc-target-err" aria-required="true">
                <p id="sc-target-err" class="text-red-600 text-sm min-h-[1rem]" aria-live="polite"></p>
              </div>

              <fieldset class="mt-2">
                <legend class="sr-only">Rounding</legend>
                <div class="segmented" role="radiogroup" aria-label="Rounding">
                  <input type="radio" id="sc-round-none" name="sc-round" value="none" checked><label for="sc-round-none">Exact</label>
                  <input type="radio" id="sc-round-nearest" name="sc-round" value="nearest"><label for="sc-round-nearest">Nearest integer</label>
                </div>
              </fieldset>

              <div class="flex gap-3 mt-2">
                <button id="btn-scale" type="button" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-md bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500">Calculate</button>
                <button id="btn-scale-reset" type="button" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-md border border-gray-300 text-gray-800 font-semibold hover:bg-gray-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500">Reset</button>
              </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Split total -->
            <section id="panel-split" role="region" aria-labelledby="panel-split-title" hidden aria-hidden="true">
              <h2 id="panel-split-title" class="font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Split a total by a ratio</h2>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div><label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" for="sp-a">First term (a) *</label><input id="sp-a" type="text" inputmode="decimal" class="w-full border rounded-md px-3 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" aria-describedby="sp-a-err" aria-required="true"><p id="sp-a-err" class="text-red-600 text-sm min-h-[1rem]" aria-live="polite"></p></div>
                <div><label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" for="sp-b">Second term (b) *</label><input id="sp-b" type="text" inputmode="decimal" class="w-full border rounded-md px-3 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" aria-describedby="sp-b-err" aria-required="true"><p id="sp-b-err" class="text-red-600 text-sm min-h-[1rem]" aria-live="polite"></p></div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-2">
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-800" for="sp-total">Total to split (T) *</label>
                <input id="sp-total" type="text" inputmode="decimal" class="w-full border rounded-md px-3 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" aria-describedby="sp-total-err" aria-required="true">
                <p id="sp-total-err" class="text-red-600 text-sm min-h-[1rem]" aria-live="polite"></p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex gap-3 mt-2">
                <button id="btn-split" type="button" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-md bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500">Calculate</button>
                <button id="btn-split-reset" type="button" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-md border border-gray-300 text-gray-800 font-semibold hover:bg-gray-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500">Reset</button>
              </div>
            </section>
          </div>

          <!-- Results -->
          <section class="mt-8 bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg" aria-live="polite" role="status">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3">Results</h2>
            <div id="results-content"><p>Enter values to see results. The results panel is reserved for output to prevent layout shift.</p></div>
          </section>
        </section>

        <!-- SEO content (kept & improved for E-E-A-T) -->
        <article class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md mt-8 prose">
          <h2>Data Source and Methodology</h2>
          <p><strong>Authoritative basis:</strong> ISO 80000-2:2019 — <em>Quantities and units — Part 2: Mathematics</em>. Definitions and identities for ratio and proportion align with this standard. (ISO, 2019.)</p>

          <h2>The Formula Explained</h2>
          <div class="formula-box" aria-label="Mathematical formulas">
            <p><strong>Simplify a:b</strong> using the greatest common divisor (GCD):</p>
            <p>$$\\text{Let } g=\\gcd(a,b)\\ ,\\quad a:b \\equiv \\frac{a}{g}:\\frac{b}{g}$$</p>
            <p><strong>Proportion equivalence & cross-multiplication</strong>:</p>
            <p>$$\\frac{a}{b}=\\frac{c}{d}\\ \\Longleftrightarrow\\ ad=bc$$</p>
            <p><strong>Solve the missing term</strong> (when defined):</p>
            <p>$$a=\\frac{bc}{d},\\quad b=\\frac{ad}{c},\\quad c=\\frac{ad}{b},\\quad d=\\frac{bc}{a}$$</p>
            <p><strong>Scaling</strong> to a target \(T\) on term \(a\): \(k=T/a\\), then \((a',b')=(ka,kb)\).</p>
            <p><strong>Split a total</strong> \(T\) by \(a:b\): \(x=\\tfrac{a}{a+b}T\\), \(y=\\tfrac{b}{a+b}T\\).</p>
          </div>

          <h2>Glossary of Variables</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>a, b</strong>: ratio terms a:b</li>
            <li><strong>c, d</strong>: second ratio for a proportion a:b = c:d</li>
            <li><strong>GCD</strong>: greatest common divisor</li>
            <li><strong>k</strong>: scaling factor; <strong>T</strong>: total; <strong>x, y</strong>: parts of T</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Worked Example</h2>
          <ol>
            <li>Simplify 18:24 → GCD = 6 → 3:4.</li>
            <li>Scale so \(a=21\): \(k=21/3=7\) → 21:28.</li>
            <li>Split \(T=350\) by 3:4: \(x=350·3/7=150\), \(y=350·4/7=200\).</li>
          </ol>

          <h2>FAQs</h2>
          <details><summary>How do I simplify a ratio with decimals?</summary><p>Multiply both terms by a power of 10 to clear decimals (e.g., 2.4:3.6 → 24:36), then divide by the GCD. The calculator automates this.</p></details>
          <details><summary>Can a ratio include zero?</summary><p>Yes: 0:n → 0:1 and n:0 → 1:0 (n&gt;0). 0:0 is undefined.</p></details>
          <details><summary>How do I solve a:b=c:d for a missing term?</summary><p>Use cross-multiplication \(ad=bc\) and isolate the unknown (e.g., \(d=bc/a\)).</p></details>
          <details><summary>What rounding does the scaler use?</summary><p>Choose exact or nearest-integer; we show exact and rounded so you see the impact.</p></details>
          <details><summary>Do you store my inputs?</summary><p>No. All calculations run in your browser.</p></details>

          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 border-t pt-4">
            Tool developed by <strong>Ugo Candido</strong>. Content verified by the <strong>CalcDomain Editorial Team</strong>.<br/>
            Last reviewed: September 14, 2025.
          </div>
        </article>
      </main>

